msgstr "Sobre el proyecto"

#: templates/core/about.html:12
msgid ""
"Welcome to your personal financial cockpit. This platform is designed to "
"give you a clear and realistic look at your long-term financial future."
msgstr ""

#: templates/core/about.html:15
msgid ""
"Our goal is to demystify complex financial planning by offering simple, "
"visual, and highly customizable tools to help you reach your goals."
msgstr ""

#: templates/core/about.html:23
msgid "Personal Data Security"
msgstr ""

#: templates/core/about.html:24
msgid ""
"Your data is only stored in your personal database and is not shared with "
"third parties."
